    <p>You are solely responsible for the content you scan, store, or share using the App. You agree not to use the App to scan, reproduce, or distribute materials protected by copyright or intellectual property rights without explicit permission from the rights holder. The Developer assumes no liability for any illegal, unauthorized, or harmful use of the App by its users.</p>

